<br>
That was before the changes in T-rods though.  Now you have the 5-minute time-limit restrictions in place.  Although I still love the spell, I'm wondering if the robe has become useful now?<br>
<br>
Do any of you find that the mod rods aren't enough now and start clicking away on a mana robe?  I know my regen is much faster than the 5-minute timer and I could easily click the robe several times and still regen to full before 5 minutes is up.<br>
<br>
Anybody using 1 of these on a regular basis?  Tough to decide if it is worth using.  Like our other magician in guild points out &quot;I die from aggro and a lack of HP, never from being OoM&quot;.<br>
